    <author>
      <name>Ryon Sherman</name>
    </author>
    <content type="html"><p>I recently updated my old static site generator, Noise, from Python 2 to Python 3.</p>
<p>Key changes:
- Ported to Python 3.8+
- Replaced insecure import with <code>importlib.util</code>
- Added proper test suite
- Modern packaging with <code>pyproject.toml</code></p></content>
